cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.AI 

The paper deals with image recognition and feature extraction, which are core topics in computer vision (cs.CV). It also introduces a new binary descriptor that improves on accuracy and time complexity, which are important considerations in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper evaluates the performance of the proposed method on standard benchmarks, which is a common practice in information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also introduces a new dataset on lepidoptera, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories.
